{"tid":1995593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國網漫家聲援港人抗爭 網上辦展覽說抗爭故事","createTime":"2020-04-30T11:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T13:09:40.000Z","uid":66992,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2af7c08f08ae9fe1d2d11efeeb290fd5ed22a2ff","tid":1995593,"uid":66992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:10:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8rpfQqJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8rpfQqJ.jpg&h=82e11edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「香港人，你們不是在孤身作戰，還有我們韓國人，一直關注香港，與你們同在，連結在一起 ... 」<br />\n<br />\n這是一群在韓國舉辦名為「香港之春」網絡漫畫展的畫家，對香港人留下的打氣感言。<br />\n<br />\n今年二月，一群韓國網絡漫畫家，透過網上眾籌，成功獲得百多人支持，籌得所需的五百萬韓圜，建造了一個網站，上載十七有關香港人抗爭的短篇網絡漫畫故事。<br />\n<br />\n這個「香港之春」網漫展覽，已於本月三號於網上免費公開展出，展期直至六月二十五日。據主辦者所說，他們取四月三日開始展覽，是因為當天是韓國濟州起義，亦稱為「4.3 事件」的紀念品。而於六月二十五日結束，是因為當天正是韓戰戰爭爆發的日子。<br />\n<br />\n如參與此展覽的漫畫家解釋，他們都是受韓國當年光州起義一事啟發，當看到港人長期不斷的示威，還有奮力抵抗暴力鎮壓的片段，都紛紛有感而發，把想跟港人道出支援的話，以畫筆描繪出來。<br />\n<br />\n這個原來只有韓語的展覽，上周五起（4.24）網站也已提供了英文翻譯，供不懂韓語的港人也能看懂那些故事內容。鼓勵大家多點瀏覽，細心欣賞那些創作，可以的話，更希望大家可以留言，感謝那些正義勇敢的韓國網絡畫家，無懼打壓，在困難之時，亦繼續為港人發聲聲援。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/stevechung413/posts/1696210893860752\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstevechung413%2Fposts%2F1696210893860752&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=4abb3d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/stevechung413/posts/1696210893860752</a><br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<strong>韓國網漫「香港之春」：</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://springhk.imweb.me/English\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspringhk.imweb.me%2FEnglish&d=u41oPESRP74RcK6mblIGZyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=8fde2a10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://springhk.imweb.me/English</a><br />\n<br />\n全部都畫得好好 有啲睇到眼濕濕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家有時間嘅可以入去 GUESTBOOK 嗰度留個言多謝韓國手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b73c36bb36c1402c4b817923b2dececc2d42718","tid":1995593,"uid":237038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:27:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d25d21d75402eef139d21de658ce4bb9d4f8896d","tid":1995593,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:30:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d103eeff2b10b984297cdbbcaf00c2e61143143","tid":1995593,"uid":177213,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"都係南韓啲人最有情有義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0395f1ff1215c6a20e07603667be5821de645da","tid":1995593,"uid":58552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:34:23.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"fab6dacdedf99aa003ad769b36ff4df734e6f36c","tid":1995593,"uid":66992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6890d44c3d8eb4084f3a68d2c2c6697319bdc00","tid":1995593,"uid":66992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:35:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93827b5a65208ba054183f1b8509ad309743728c","tid":1995593,"uid":160176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T12:40:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"256f9e7d3660dd6d67cc27e6650a73e17c5d871f","tid":1995593,"uid":66992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:25:36.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"808dd2b75ca392fd81d55f9b570c499a6f8debd1","tid":1995593,"uid":160257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T13:26:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\